{"tid":2305871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★羅致光：按人數來計，是相當多人有興趣去大灣區！不擔心那些人回不回香港！","createTime":"2020-11-30T04:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T13:16:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b1396e1788d0d2184780b73817ffaf2a6c7f91","tid":2305871,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示：「雖然不是很多年輕人，按比例會有興趣到灣區，但如果按人數來計，基本上都是相當多人，所以二千這數目未必滿足需求。我們希望特別有大的企業會騰出就業機會。我不擔心那二千人回不回香港，香港有機會、香港有吸引就會回來，所以不是要綁住那些人，反而讓年輕人擴闊視野。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5fc45dd334b031122ee02e43/施政報告提出大灣區青年就業計劃-羅致光冀明年首季正式推出\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5fc45dd334b031122ee02e43%2F%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89%E5%86%80%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%96%E5%AD%A3%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=eb94137b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5fc45dd334b031122ee02e43/施政報告提出大灣區青年就業計劃-羅致光冀明年首季正式推出</a>"},{"pid":"50d42f83be44179acdfdd78d07982eaea68aa4dc","tid":2305871,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"一去不回？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca89b0171aabedf4325994a6a55b08032bb41b8","tid":2305871,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji